1.notes: Scenario 3: The flexibility of the MAD Builder arises from the capability to upload your own images and use them as options, cues or cue values. In this case, we consider the task in which we ask people to choose between two food products. The first cue is the amount of calories (numbers), the second is the price ($), and the third cue is the country of origin (images of flags). Since it is a preferential choice, we will not estimate how correct the answer is and will not give participants any feedback.
